The annotations above ensures the ID variable works like an entity&#39;s identification. Now as it represents a unique value, you can make POST requests without passing any value for the id because it&#39;s an auto-generated field.

For PUT requests you&#39;re gonna always have to specify the id once JPA needs to fetch the object from the DB to make any change.

