The [@AfterMapping](http://mapstruct.org/documentation/stable/reference/html/#customizing-mappings-with-before-and-after) annotation means that the method will be imported inside the generated source, after the mapping of the properties. Thus, the Mapper implementation will be like this,
  
    @Component
